n如果是這樣 你不要悲哀 共和國的土壤裡有我們付出的愛<br />\n如果是這樣 你不要悲哀 共和國的土壤裡有我們付出的愛<br />\n<br />\n如果是這樣 你不要悲哀 共和國的旗幟上有我們血染的風采<br />\n如果是這樣 你不要悲哀 共和國的旗幟上有我們血染的風采<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n如果有人話：「呢啲係鄰國嘅事，我哋顧掂自己香港，爭取真普選先」<br />\n請你哋block Q咗呢啲人，果啲係五毛嚟<br />\n因為而家係鄰國過去咁多年每日每分每秒搞鳩緊我哋<br />\n<br />\n鄰國愈亂，自顧不暇，各省地方勢力掘起，對我哋有利</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"00de123392c2e5d141d3d3360f08e972b0d4bddd","tid":1580030,"uid":117906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T00:59:46.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">[公海 文宣 行動整合] 9.29全球抗赤納粹集會<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1579667\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1579667</a><br />\n全世界一齊對準ChiNazi極權！</span></span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BZiskWr.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBZiskWr.png&h=b85bf973&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">9.29 Global AntiChiNazi 文宣、資訊、行動整合Channel</span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/AntiChinazi929\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FAntiChinazi929&d=gqDWnnaI%2FM4dwC7GJUFj5d5k9s62d79lhUbErROZgj4%3D&h=f018627c\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/AntiChinazi929</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>9.29 Global AntiChiNazi 公海</strong></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/NfHvOU5TXSG9DxQIRNkxLQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FNfHvOU5TXSG9DxQIRNkxLQ&d=gqDWnnaI%2FM4dwC7GJUFj5d5k9s62d79lhUbErROZgj4%3D&h=c5cc2f1a\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/NfHvOU5TXSG9DxQIRNkxLQ</a>"},{"pid":"d4a3f4ed634d674425269db97c88052790f7fa0b","tid":1580030,"uid":117906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T01:00:46.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">[公海 文宣 行動整合] 9.29全球抗赤納粹集會<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/15796